metadata.name: Insomnia
metadata.description:
I'm exhausted and want to sleep, but I can't sleep. The cycle of thoughts is twisted so much that it is impossible to concentrate on any of them. Fragments of visual images and words add up to some kind of fuzzy picture that haunts me. I want to sleep.

Size: 500x350mm

Buying a physical canvas is available by arrangement.

Materials: Custom plywood canvas, magazine clippings, receipt paper, spray paint, ink, acrylic.
